        "\n",
        "#Unit Sample Sequence\n",
        "\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "from scipy import signal\n",
        "\n",
        "n = 5\n",
        "n0 = 2\n",
        "imp = signal.unit_impulse(n, n0)\n",
        "\n",
        "fig = plt.figure()\n",
        "ax = fig.add_subplot(1, 1, 1)\n",
        "\n",
        "plt.stem(np.arange(0,n),'r', markerfmt='ro', basefmt='k')\n",
        "plt.xlabel\n",
        "plt.ylabel\n",
        "plt.title\n",
        "plt.show()"
      ]

        "\n",
        "#Unit Step Signal\n",
        "\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "\n",
        "def unit_step_sequence(n0, n1, n2):\n",
        "\n",
        "    n = np.arange(n1,n2+1)\n",
        "    u = np.zeros_like(n)\n",
        "    u[n >= n0] = 1\n",
        "    return u\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "n0 = 2.5\n",
        "n1 = -2\n",
        "n2 = 7\n",
        "u = unit_step_sequence(n0, n1, n2)\n",
        "\n",
        "fig = plt.figure()\n",
        "ax = fig.add_subplot(1, 1, 1)\n",
        "\n",
        "plt.stem(np.arange(n1,n2+1), u,'r', markerfmt='o', basefmt='k', use_line_collection=True)\n",
        "plt.xlabel('n')\n",
        "plt.ylabel(r'$u[n]$')\n",
        "plt.grid(True)\n",
        "plt.show()"
      ]

        "# Unit Ramp Signal\n",
        "\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "\n",
        "t = np.linspace(-3,7, 500)\n",
        "\n",
        "r_t = np.maximum(0, t)\n",
        "\n",
        "plt.plot(t, r_t, label='Unit Ramp Signal r(t)')\n",
        "plt.xlabel('n')\n",
        "plt.ylabel('Amplitude')\n",
        "plt.grid(True)\n",
        "plt.legend()\n",
        "plt.show()"
      ]

        "# Exponential Signal\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "\n",
        "A = 1.5\n",
        "tau = 1.0\n",
        "t = np.linspace(0,10)\n",
        "\n",
        "x_t = A * np.exp(-t / tau)\n",
        "plt.plot(t, x_t)\n",
        "plt.title('Exponential Signal')\n",
        "plt.xlabel('n')\n",
        "plt.ylabel('Amplitude')\n",
        "plt.grid(True)\n",
        "plt.show()"
      ]
    },

        "# Triangular Signal\n",
        "\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "T = 3\n",
        "A = 1\n",
        "t = np.linspace(0, 5*T,500)\n",
        "\n",
        "triangular_signal = A * (1 - 2 * np.abs((t/T) % 1 - 0.5))\n",
        "plt.plot(t, triangular_signal, label = 'Triangular Signal')\n",
        "plt.xlabel('n')\n",
        "plt.ylabel('Amplitude')\n",
        "plt.grid(True)\n",
        "plt.legend()\n",
        "plt.show()"
      ],
